Partezum varder bacvac',
Kspasen soxaki,
Arranc soxak t'arramac',
Karot en psaki։

|	Ardyoq o՞v e', durrn e' t'akum,
|	A՜x, sirts kdogha,
|	Im siruhis o՞wr e' gnum,
|	A՜x, sirts kxagha։

Getaki aliqnery'
Gnum en xaytalov,
Sirahari achqeric
Artasuq t'ap'elov։

Siruhin tany' nstac'՝
Spasum e' yarin,
Qnary' dzerrqin brrnac'՝
Nvagum lalagin։

T'it'erry' tshragi mot
Shrjum e' andadar,
Minch ir verj sirakarot
Chuni na or, dadar։

Siruhin tany' nstac'
Grum e' namakner,
Xist trtum kanckacne
Ir geghecik orer։
